The paper investigates the capacity scaling of multicell massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of spatial correlation on the performance of massive MIMO, which is a topic related to signal processing (cs.SI) and wireless communications (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a statistical spatial despreading technique, which is a topic related to communication complexity (cs.COM).
